T02TD3598E:224b-1: badzra shrim kham l'a s'a dha nam /
T02TD3598E:224b-3: rdo rje lcags sgrog gi sgrub thabs /
T02TD3598E:224b-4: rdo rje lcags sgrog ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3598E:224b-5: sngon du gsungs pa'i cho gas stong pa nyid du bsgoms pa'i rjes la /
T02TD3598E:224b-6: sna tshogs chu skyes dang nyi ma la gnas pa'i h'um yig ljang gu las skyes pa'i sku mdog ljang gu zhal gsum pa phyag brgyad pa /
T02TD3598E:224b-7: zhal dang po cung zad bzhad pa /
T02TD3598E:224b-8: g-yas ser skya la spyan ser skya dang ldan pa /
T02TD3598E:224b-9: g-yon pa dmar zhing khro gnyer can mche ba gtsigs pa /
T02TD3598E:224b-10: g-yas kyi phyag bzhi rnams su mi 'jigs pa dang /
T02TD3598E:224b-12: rdo rje lcags sgrog dang mda' bsnams pa /
T02TD3598E:224b-13: g-yon gyi phyag bzhi rnams su khrag gis gang ba'i thod pa dang /
T02TD3598E:224b-17: rol pa'i stabs kyis bzhugs pa /
T02TD3598E:224b-18: byi la'i pags pas stod g-yogs byas pa /
T02TD3598E:224b-19: don yod grub pas dbu brgyan pa /
T02TD3598E:224b-20: dbu skra ser skya gyen du 'khyil par bsams la /
T02TD3598E:224b-21: aom badzra shrim kha le h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD3598E:224b-22: zhes pa'i sngags bzlas par bya'o //
T02TD3598E:224b-23: 'di ni man ngag gi rim pa'i nang nas 'byung ba'i rdo rje lcags sgrog gi sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
